a resets CNS.</p>\n<h3>Schema FAQ</h3>\n<p><strong>How long for a full Appalachian Trail section hike?</strong><br>1-4 weeks per state. Full: 5-7 months only.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#39;s the daily mileage on the AT?</strong><br>10-20 miles. Avg 14. Terrain varies.</p>\n<p><strong>Can you hike the AT in under 5 months?</strong><br>Yes, elites do 150 days. Most need 6 months. Train smart.</p>\n		How long does it take to hike the Appalachian Trail? - Atlas Mountains hiking	2	Guides	{}	Atlas Hikes	Mountain Guide	/svg/hiker.svg	t	f	0	How long does it take to hike the Appalachian Trail?	How Long Does It Take to Hike the Appalachian Trail?\r \r Thru-hiking the full 2,190-mile Appalachian Trail takes 5-7 months. Most cover 10-15 miles daily...	https://atlashikes.com/blogs/how-long-does-it-take-to-hike-the-appalachian-trail	2026-01-16 19:31:56.78	2026-03-31 09:32:23.554236	2026-03-31 09:32:23.554236
